{"tid":1028943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"車CAM條女嗌得好淫","createTime":"2019-02-20T01:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T01:37:11.000Z","uid":225464,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6f9337a2fa828388f251e366aea6816ebf957a7d","tid":1028943,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:04:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>私家車屯公跣胎炒壆 目擊女激動驚呼成「重點」</strong><br />\n<br />\n片LINK：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Sav1R2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Sav1R2&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=e11f7586\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Sav1R2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190220/photo/bkn-20190220081520018-0220_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190220081819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190220081520018-0220_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190220081819&h=93e8043e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽得出佢當時非常驚慌！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日屯門公路有私家車疑因路面濕滑，意外跣胎自炒。有目擊者頓時嚇至大聲尖叫︰「BB，BB，停呀停呀，BB」。<br />\n<br />\n網民鍾一鋒將片段轉載到Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」，畫面所見，周二（19日）凌晨1時許，有私家車在屯門公路近汀九橋一段行駛，惟轉彎時疑跣胎失控，扭了幾個S字後，撞向橋壆自炒。<br />\n<br />\n目擊意外的後車女乘客頓時大驚，向旁邊的司機疾呼︰「喂！停呀！停呀BB！BB，BB停呀停呀！停呀！啊」！<br />\n<br />\n有網友表示該位置經常發生意外：「呢個位落雨真係成日炒，好邪」、「扭咗咁多吓，最後都係救唔番」。不少網民則「錯重點」︰「呢段片女主角嘅聲音導航就非常出眾」、「成條片淨聽聲唔睇畫面，係另一個故事」。<br />\n<br />\n想知當時情況係點？即刻睇片！"},{"pid":"73ca603dcdb4c3209f546d0235742f19956e9dd7","tid":1028943,"uid":228963,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:05:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b6359010645e360834f2b6c7197e6ed457c143c","tid":1028943,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65188c19bf34c05de7840a3d46a0b1105a935e93","tid":1028943,"uid":224952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:24:33.000Z","msg":"諗住一心聽條女叫啦 屌你老尾個旁白阻撚住晒<br />\n咁撚得閒作埋啲鳩歌伏也乜撚野"},{"pid":"8d0a091f04b2be994d798ba9a4df40ce9106c28f","tid":1028943,"uid":12946,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得東方依D改歌詞，一定都唔好笑，仲好撚煩？"},{"pid":"83a16ddd2e07850e26993605f6f1e5150d480111","tid":1028943,"uid":145126,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8d0a091f04b2be994d798ba9a4df40ce9106c28f","tid":1028943,"uid":12946,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得東方依D改歌詞，一定都唔好笑，仲好撚煩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:29:34.000Z","msg":"無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好柒好笑喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b85439375fc2e6634a9ed3bc6d65bcd94626e3d","tid":1028943,"uid":40125,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:29:48.000Z","msg":"On9方向報 我想聽把聲 唔係啲閪歌"},{"pid":"10cc824193e20db703445b53d22c0da88a019f21","tid":1028943,"uid":179283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}